Class WkfNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.axelor.db.Model
      • com.axelor.auth.db.AuditableModel
        • com.axelor.studio.db.WkfNode

  • @Entity
public class WkfNode
extends com.axelor.auth.db.AuditableModel
    This is workflow node and it represents status of object linked with workflow. It is also used to generate menu entry based on status.
